register

public static void register(String key,
                            Operation operation)
Register a new operation. The built in operations cannot be overridden. Key should be a single character. This method is not synchronized; it is not recommended that registrations be allowed from multiple threads or while multiple threads are expanding templates. Perform all registrations before any template expansion occurs.
